data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod Home nestled in the Bristol Hills! Rustic open concept floor plan with cathedral ceilings, cozy wood stove, and sliding glass door overlooking the big back yard. First floor living with 3 bedrooms and 1 1/2 Baths. Loft has room for office or play room, plus tons of storage space. Pole Barn built in 2010 has 2 propane furnaces & 100 amp service. Additional 30 amp hook-up & water hydrant for RV's. New well and pump 2000. Furnace 2015. House was renovated in 1998 - square footage now 1,640 per appraisal. Great location close to Honeoye Lake, Bristol Mountain, Canandaigua, Victor and all the Finger Lakes has to offer. Don't miss this opportunity!
